{
  "key": "CT-622",
  "url": "https://next-t-code.atlassian.net/browse/CT-622",
  "summary": "[FE] Metamask FE integration (mob+desktop)",
  "status": "Testing",
  "priority": "Normal",
  "assignee": "Panda Sensei",
  "description": {
    "type": "doc",
    "version": 1,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Within the scope of this task it`s needed to integrate the Metamask as registration&authorization method."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Task:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "attrs": {
          "order": 1
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Connect Frontend SDK (wagmi + viem or ethers.js). "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Add Metamask button to the registration&login form. (Strapi)  "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "If",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " MetaMask extension is not installed"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "then",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " show popup over registration form (the Metamask integration decision)."
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The popup suggests the client to download the Metamask extension. "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "mediaSingle",
                "attrs": {
                  "width": 626,
                  "widthType": "pixel",
                  "layout": "align-start"
                },
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "media",
                    "attrs": {
                      "type": "file",
                      "id": "fce4209d-2f53-43f8-951e-f55186a00982",
                      "alt": "\u0421\u043d\u0438\u043c\u043e\u043a \u044d\u043a\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0430 2025-11-25 \u0432 15.43.17.png",
                      "collection": "",
                      "height": 770,
                      "width": 804
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "If ",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "the metamask extension is installed"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "then",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " the login&auth flow happens "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "and",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " the loader appears on registration&login button "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "and",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " disables it during the process"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Integrate BE API.  "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Documentation:",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "https://next-t-code.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/CTD/pages/513769484/001.+Crypto-Wallet+Registration+Authorization+OAUTH",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "link",
                        "attrs": {
                          "href": "https://www.google.com/url?q=https://next-t-code.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/CTD/pages/513769484/001.%2BCrypto-Wallet%2BRegistration%2BAuthorization%2BOAUTH&sa=D&source=calendar&ust=1767534815825539&usg=AOvVaw0eD6RTHOvayx5QVspeLPDt"
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "underline"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "inlineCard",
                    "attrs": {
                      "url": "https://docs.metamask.io/wallet/how-to/sign-data/siwe/"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Design -"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "inlineCard",
                    "attrs": {
                      "url": "https://www.figma.com/design/qkzG2IGMeL6JEpJSmIEQxE/Minebit?node-id=90-35271&p=f&t=NDTIQb5GThC42UNx-0"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Tech note:",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "hardBreak"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1. Research which SDK should be connected or if SDK is required at all."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
